      • getEditability

        public IEditability getEditability()
        Specifies the editability status for the slot.

        NOTE: If the slot is a special "disjuncts-slots" attached to a disjunction-frame (see IFrame for details), then editability will always be IEditability.CONCRETE_ONLY) on both assertions and queries, despite the editability status of the slot-type being CEditability.DEFAULT, which will always be the case for disjuncts-slots.

        Returns:
        Editability status for slot
